b(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Afore offers standard factory warranty which is valid 5 years from the &amp;nbsp;date of &amp;nbsp;installation and no more than 5 and a half years from the delivery date from Afore.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;1.Product Quality Standards and Warranty&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;1.1 Afore inverters comply with local safety regulations related to the national grid and grid standards.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;1.2 The inverter warranty is decided by Afore and its distributor.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;1.3 Spare parts warranty is valid 3 months (beginning from &amp;nbsp;the date of shipment), during the warranty period, Afore is&amp;nbsp;responsible for the replacement.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.aforenergy.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181115/1542241733.png&quot; title=&quot;1542241733.png&quot; alt=&quot;1542160731(1).png&quot; width=&quot;737&quot; height=&quot;183&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;1.4 After &amp;nbsp;the &amp;nbsp;products leaving &amp;nbsp;the &amp;nbsp;factory, the &amp;nbsp;appearance &amp;nbsp;damage (scratches, &amp;nbsp;rust, chemical &amp;nbsp;damage) &amp;nbsp;is beyond&amp;nbsp;warranty.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;2.Warranty Exceptions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.1 Damage or lose to inverter or accessory caused by logistics.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.2 Inverter &amp;nbsp;failure caused by &amp;nbsp;non-compliance with &amp;nbsp;national utility grid &amp;nbsp;standard &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;which &amp;nbsp;lead to eg. &amp;nbsp;abnormal grid voltage, grid frequency etc.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.3 Inverter malfunction or damage caused by non-professional or non-qualified personnel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.4 Failure to observe the user manual, the installation guide, and the maintenance regulations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.5 Remove or damage warranty seal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.6 Change or remove specification label, serial number (SN).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.7 Product &amp;nbsp;malfunction or &amp;nbsp;damage &amp;nbsp;due to &amp;nbsp;disobey to &amp;nbsp;relevant laws &amp;nbsp;and regulations &amp;nbsp;or technical &amp;nbsp;requirements in&amp;nbsp;power plant design, construction or installation works.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.8 Solar panels’ input parameters exceed the inverter’s allowed range.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.9 Product malfunction or damage due to installation on movable device or in vibration occasions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.10 Failure or damage caused by corrosion, lightning and other natural damage or force majeure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.11 Unauthorized alteration or disassembly of the product.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2.13&amp;nbsp;Low electricity generation &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;because &amp;nbsp;of inverter self-protection caused by environmental reasons (such&amp;nbsp;as the installation environment, natural environment, grid environment, etc.) is not a quality problem.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;3.Repair and Replacement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;3.1 When a &amp;nbsp;failure occurs, the user should &amp;nbsp;check and record from &amp;nbsp;the screen display the error &amp;nbsp;code, DC voltage, AC&amp;nbsp;voltage data or phenomena ect., then contact your local dealer.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;